00:27:45,076 --> 00:27:45,497
I had to cut.

677
00:27:45,497 --> 00:27:51,919
Very briefly, for technical stuff, when it comes to students, make sure that you study

678
00:27:51,919 --> 00:27:53,100
up on those things that I had mentioned.

