00:28:27,078 --> 00:28:28,919
before you can come into the industry

692
00:28:28,919 --> 00:28:30,880
and get experience making games,

693
00:28:30,880 --> 00:28:32,861
is those projects are the magical ones.

694
00:28:32,861 --> 00:28:35,783
I have a lot of other things that I could say.

695
00:28:35,783 --> 00:28:36,683
Let's talk afterwards.

