00:28:47,412 --> 00:28:50,374
issues and how you deal with people that just don't want

702
00:28:50,374 --> 00:28:52,615
to do anything, and those sorts of issues,

703
00:28:52,615 --> 00:28:54,977
which are exactly the same if you're in college

704
00:28:54,977 --> 00:28:56,398
or you're at Ubisoft.

705
00:28:56,398 --> 00:28:56,578
Yeah.

