00:29:23,862 --> 00:29:28,024
Do you know of any red flags for both the interviewer

717
00:29:28,024 --> 00:29:30,566
and the interviewee that kind of dictate,

718
00:29:30,566 --> 00:29:34,068
oh, this might be a bad job, or oh, this is a bad candidate,

