00:30:21,089 --> 00:30:23,110
that they want in terms of utility theory, but if I say,

740
00:30:23,110 --> 00:30:26,212
here's a little project, build me a little utility system

741
00:30:26,212 --> 00:30:30,255
for these autonomous agents so that I have a virtual city working,

742
00:30:30,255 --> 00:30:32,697
then they're going to be able to do it or they're going to fall apart.

